00:47:30,699 --> 00:47:33,269
Itu lagu kesukaan nenekku.

695
00:47:33,370 --> 00:47:34,370
Benarkah?

696
00:47:35,469 --> 00:47:38,640
Astaga, nenekku

697
00:47:39,640 --> 00:47:41,880
sangat menyukai lagu itu juga.

698
00:47:41,880 --> 00:47:43,380
Di mana nenek Kakek?

